txt.en: Good places to place traps can be found around the battlefield.\n\nYou should place traps around the battlefield.
Placed many traps on the battlefield.

Thyra holds out a trap made from the jaws of an avanc from Misthallow.\n\n'What do you think? I made them myself. Yrsa thought they might be useful so I brought them with us. These traps would catch the enemy if buried on the battlefield. Would you take these traps and bury them for me when you next go into battle?'
You have successfully placed many of Thyra's traps on the battlefield. Those in the war effort will be thankful for all that you have accomplished.
The Beorning Thyra has constructed traps to set upon the battlefield, made from the jaws of avanc.
